## HTML — nunca cachear, siempre fresco
/*.html
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=0, must-revalidate

/
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=0, must-revalidate

## JS y CSS minificados — cachear agresivamente (nombre cambia con cada build)
/assets/js/*.min.js
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=31536000, immutable

/assets/css/*.min.css
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=31536000, immutable

## Imágenes — cachear 1 semana
/assets/img/*
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=604800

/assets/img/**/*
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=604800
